Package com.microsoft.tfs.core.pendingcheckin.events

Interface Summary
AffectedTeamProjectsChangedListener Defines an interface for listeners of the AffectedTeamProjectsChangedEvent.
CheckedPendingChangesChangedListener Defines an interface for listeners of the CheckedPendingChangesChangedEvent.
CheckedWorkItemsChangedListener Defines an interface for listeners of the CheckedWorkItemsChangedEvent.
CommentChangedListener Defines an interface for listeners of the CommentChangedEvent.
NotesChangedListener Defines an interface for listeners of the NotesChangedEvent.
 

Class Summary
AffectedTeamProjectsChangedEvent Event fired when the collection of affected team projects changes in a PendingCheckinPendingChanges object.
CheckedPendingChangesChangedEvent Event fired when the pending changes that are "checked" in the user interface changes in a PendingCheckinPendingChanges object.
CheckedWorkItemsChangedEvent Event fired when the work items that are "checked" in the user interface changes in a PendingCheckinWorkItems object.
CommentChangedEvent Event fired when the user's check-in comment text changes in a PendingCheckinWorkItems object.
NotesChangedEvent Event fired when the user's check-in notes change in a PendingCheckinNotes object.
